### Test Officer Performance Endpoint
### Requirements: 9.1, 9.2, 9.3, 9.4, 9.5

### 1. Test as Officer (should see only own metrics)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/gov/analytics/officer-performance?period=30
Authorization: Bearer {{officer_token}}

### 2. Test as Admin (should see all officers in agency)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/gov/analytics/officer-performance?period=30
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### 3. Test as Super Admin (should see all officers across agencies)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/gov/analytics/officer-performance?period=30
Authorization: Bearer {{super_admin_token}}

### 4. Test with 90-day period
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/gov/analytics/officer-performance?period=90
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### 5. Test with 365-day period
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/gov/analytics/officer-performance?period=365
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### 6. Test cache (should return cached data on second request)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/gov/analytics/officer-performance?period=30
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### 7. Test without authentication (should fail with 401)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/gov/analytics/officer-performance?period=30

### 8. Test with invalid period (should fail with 400)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/gov/analytics/officer-performance?period=60
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
